        <mj-column width="100%">
          <mj-text color="#637381" font-size="16px"> Dear Members of the Hotchkiss Community, <br> <br> The time has come to announce the CXXII Editorial Board of <i>The Hotchkiss Record.</i> The current executive board and faculty advisors are extremely proud of all the work done by these individuals
            and are confident in their ability to continue to make <i>The Record</i> the best newspaper produced by Hotchkiss students. Please congratulate the new editors when you see them.</mj-text>
          <mj-image src="https://graphics.thehr.org/TheRecord122MastheadFinal.jpg"
            alt="The Masthead of The CXXII Board" align="center" />
          <mj-text color="#637381" font-size="16px"> While the official changeover date for the staff is still not for a couple of weeks, training for some editors has already begun. We hope you enjoy the final issues under the CXXI board.<br> <br> <b>Nicholas Lorentzen,</b> <br>
            On Behalf of The CXXI Executive Editorial Board of <i>The Record</i></mj-text>
